My name is Greg Dlubacz. I have been working as a UI/UX designer
since 2008. I'm fuelled with passion for effective, unique, pixel-perfect 
and simple solutions. In my free time I help other designers with
creating freebies like this one. My previous Flowchart Kit for Sketch
has been downloaded more than 300.000 times. You can check it out
here uxflow.co

If you are interested in working together, please don’t hesitate to 
contact me hello@gregdlubacz.com

You can find me on:
Dribbble: https://dribbble.com/gregdlubacz
